thread.title: Treasury to Sell $96 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $96 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $96 billion in securities next week. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $51 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Dec. 7, 2017, maturing June 7, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PJ2.
Also, $45 billion in 26-week bills, dated March 8, 2018, maturing Sept. 6,...
